This lemma can be removed because `of_fixedField_normal_subgroup` can be directly proved using `normal_iff_forall_map_le'`.

```suggestion
    apply normal_iff_forall_map_le'.mpr
    intro σ x ⟨a, ha, hax⟩ τ
    rw [← hax]
    calc _ = (σ * σ⁻¹ * τ.1 * σ) a := by rw [mul_inv_cancel]; rfl
      _ = _ := by nth_rw 2 [← ha ⟨_ , (Subgroup.Normal.conj_mem hn τ.1 τ.2 σ⁻¹)⟩]; rfl
```
This lemma should be moved to the file related to `Subgroup`.
